          <p class="reveal">In 2021, COVID collided with PTSD.</p>
          <p class="reveal">My cognition fragmented in measurable ways — memory disrupted, threat detection hyperactivated, self-model corrupted.</p>
          <p class="reveal">As a security engineer, I recognized the pattern.</p>
          <p class="reveal text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold"><span class="gradient-text">The same failure modes I'd expect from a targeted BCI attack.</span></p>
          <p class="reveal">Except no device was involved.</p>
          <p class="reveal">That question became this research.</p>
        </div>
